div.bibl:
[
                            Ratnagotra­vibhāgavyākhyā
                        ]  theg pa chen po rgyud bla ma’i bstan bcos rnam par bshad pa (Mahāyānottara­tantra­śāstra). Toh 4025, Degé Tengyur vol. 123 (sems tsam, phi), folios 74.b–129.a.

gloss.term:
These are listed as nine: thinking that one’s enemy has harmed, is harming, or will harm oneself;
                                thinking that one’s enemy has harmed, is harming, or will harm one’s friend; and thinking that someone has helped, is
                                helping, or will help one’s enemy.
